snippet.title: Adoptive parents charged in missing child's murder; Freed sex offender re-arrested - TCD Crime Check
snippet.description:
In True Crime Daily's newest podcast series "Crime Check," Stephanie Harlowe brings you true crime news and updates in quick, bite-size videos. 
In this episode: A Hawaiian couple is charged with murdering their 6-year-old adopted daughter, whose body has not been recovered (0:15).
The suspect in a Cleveland cold-case bank robbery inspired by the movie "The Thomas Crown Affair" is identified after his death (5:54).
And a convicted sex-offender is arrested and charged with attacking a Central Park jogger within two days of his release from prison (9:31).

Stephanie Harlowe: https://www.youtube.com/c/StephanieHarlowe
